{"tid":849169,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[pkm]幻之精靈「美錄坦」在Pokémon GO出現","createTime":"2018-10-05T13:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T08:01:06.000Z","uid":181318,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e13b780893735f66dee8794684f3884daf879555","tid":849169,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"至今從未有人見過的新寶可夢，其存在得到了證實。<br />\n這種寶可夢的名字叫做「美錄坦」。<br />\n據說在『Pok&eacute;mon GO』中陸續有人目擊到由百變怪變身而成的「美錄坦」。到底怎樣才能遇到這種寶可夢呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/05/sldfcO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2FsldfcO.png&h=c3a24ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.portal-pokemon.com/special/pika_vee/tc/20180925/img/image_03_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.portal-pokemon.com%2Fspecial%2Fpika_vee%2Ftc%2F20180925%2Fimg%2Fimage_03_1.png&h=15fc0f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由液態金屬構成的身體<br />\n「美錄坦」的身體大部分由液態金屬構成，形狀極具流動性。牠能用液態的手腳侵蝕金屬，將之吸收進體內。<br />\n<br />\n從體內產生的電能<br />\n「美錄坦」能把從外部吸收的金屬轉化成電能。這些電能除了用來維持牠的身體機能外，還能從眼睛發射出去攻擊對手。<br />\n<br />\n豐富的表情<br />\n「美錄坦」好奇心旺盛，對所有事物都非常感與趣。<br />\n性情非常天真無邪，而且表情十分豐富。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.portal-pokemon.com/special/pika_vee/tc/20180925/img/image_01_1.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.portal-pokemon.com%2Fspecial%2Fpika_vee%2Ftc%2F20180925%2Fimg%2Fimage_01_1.png&d=OgPaOMxrdDGmmfKz3VWl6eargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=d2713031\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.portal-pokemon.com/special/pika_vee/tc/20180925/img/image_01_1.png</a><br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n<br />\n最近先睇到<br />\n個設計衰撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n螺絲帽都得 咁我指甲夾都得啦仆街"},{"pid":"f19e0c97980297bc7e3199b06ce4e44af7116cce","tid":849169,"uid":213196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.